title: Tech View: Nifty forms bearish candle; support seen at 17,250-300 levels - Economic Times
content: Tech View: Nifty forms bearish candle; support seen at 17,250-300 levels  Economic Times
description: Nifty50 has given up almost all the gains of the last two trading sessions. In this process, it also filled the bullish gap placed in the zone of 17,339-306 level
